description: The fund may invest in common stock of U.S. large-, mid-, and small-capitalization companies and ETFs. It also may invest to a lesser extent in American Depositary Receipts ("ADRs") representing foreign company stock. Under normal circumstances, 70-80% of the fund's net assets, plus borrowings for investment purposes, will be invested in equity securities. The fund is non-diversified.
name: Cabot Growth ETF
